      • DATAFLOW_DISPLAY_NODE

        public static final java.lang.String DATAFLOW_DISPLAY_NODE
        A tag added to "data flow display nodes". A data flow display node concept does not exist outside of Jimple, except for the acceptable instance variable accesses. In some analyses it is important to identify the data flow display node as having no significant analysis value.
